            <title>18.5 小时长续航 + 左右自动摆头：小米桌面移动风扇 129 → 96 元国补发车</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/948/197.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/948/197.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Sat, 09 May 2026 07:31:12 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p>小米米家桌面移动风扇发布于 2022 年，<a href="https://c.duomai.com/track.php?aid=4705&amp;dm_fid=16052&amp;euid=&amp;site_id=261624&amp;t=https%3a%2f%2fm.xiaomiyoupin.com%2fdetail%3fgid%3d154514" target="_blank">小米有品</a>日常售价 129 元。</p><p>今日阿里自营【<strong>天猫优品官方旗舰店</strong>】报价 299 元，下单立减 45 元 + 领取 149 元优惠券，叠加 5% 政府补贴，实付 99.75 元包邮再补货。</p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>点击下方卡片后 → 点击淘宝 App 右上角三个点“<span class="font-color-orangered"><strong>…</strong></span>” → 点击弹出页面右下角<span class="font-color-orangered"><strong>淘金币</strong></span> → 下单实付 95.95 元：</p></li></ul><dir class=""><a contenteditable="false" href="https://uland.taobao.com/coupon/edetail?e=9Rse2FpeRAClhHvvyUNXZfh8CuWt5YH5OVuOuRD5gLJMmdsrkidbOWBzzpT26idJQ%2BI4UKe9QnuVtEUq4GOHfIlBdJhjw5L6Nb7syrXP4H0WuZY2ZfqBqU%2BOE0y3M3r1OyyF04DJLzXyMW3eIAWKRa6LeGhgJY%2B%2FxrWOm542iF3mhpDhiQUdsCHDJFv4HWtF082Vdr6P6lk9myuFDH3V60ob9ZRYa9bbqpXc9vysLag2hHMFUUWA%2FQpvhuGuJemkhJFPgaJn9UCxv6%2BLvWntiLcZelJt%2BzjyvWG%2B5%2BQfHiRlz%2BxnzEXEeq3iwv1OGJmrstyaVXyRn59LUGU7O58vwWUFFgz3RBVH&amp;traceId=215046d917783115754246114e0d59&amp;&amp;union_lens=lensId:TAPI@1778311575@0be36ad6_1661_19e0ba137db_0cca@01" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/5/98e9b97d-b84b-4fdd-84cb-cd901e9e1ff3.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="18.5 小时长续航 + 左右自动摆头：小米桌面移动风扇 129 → 96 元国补发车" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">天猫</span><span class="card-name">小米 桌面移动风扇</span></span><span class="card-abstract">桌面手持二合一</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">双重补贴 95.95 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">领 149 元券</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p>米家桌面移动风扇采用洁白外观，旋钮为橙色设计，支持桌面、手持两用，<span class="accentTextColor">整机净重 0.67kg</span>，底盘直径 87mm。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="427" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2022/5/4ae24191-a5c0-40cd-8eb5-2994c08accc6.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="18.5 小时长续航 + 左右自动摆头：小米桌面移动风扇 129 → 96 元国补发车" width="762" /></p><p>该风扇配备了 <span class="accentTextColor">4000mAh 电池</span>，一档风速下续航可达 18.5 小时，采用 USB-C 接口充电，可用充电宝供电。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="420" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2022/5/7dcc8297-ed72-4a40-80d1-bc90aa25f1a8.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="18.5 小时长续航 + 左右自动摆头：小米桌面移动风扇 129 → 96 元国补发车" width="762" /></p><p>此外，该风扇的噪音为 34dB (A)，采用直流无刷电机，搭载 7 片大面积翼型剖面羽叶，仿生飞鸟翅膀设计，将风团更均匀切割为细碎气流，<span class="accentTextColor">风量最高可达 6m³ / min</span>。</p><p>该风扇还支持<span class="accentTextColor">垂直手动调节摆头、左右 90° 自动摆头</span>，可调 4 档风速，网罩可拆卸等。</p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://uland.taobao.com/coupon/edetail?e=9Rse2FpeRAClhHvvyUNXZfh8CuWt5YH5OVuOuRD5gLJMmdsrkidbOWBzzpT26idJQ%2BI4UKe9QnuVtEUq4GOHfIlBdJhjw5L6Nb7syrXP4H0WuZY2ZfqBqU%2BOE0y3M3r1OyyF04DJLzXyMW3eIAWKRa6LeGhgJY%2B%2FxrWOm542iF3mhpDhiQUdsCHDJFv4HWtF082Vdr6P6lk9myuFDH3V60ob9ZRYa9bbqpXc9vysLag2hHMFUUWA%2FQpvhuGuJemkhJFPgaJn9UCxv6%2BLvWntiLcZelJt%2BzjyvWG%2B5%2BQfHiRlz%2BxnzEXEeq3iwv1OGJmrstyaVXyRn59LUGU7O58vwWUFFgz3RBVH&amp;traceId=215046d917783115754246114e0d59&amp;&amp;union_lens=lensId:TAPI@1778311575@0be36ad6_1661_19e0ba137db_0cca@01" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/5/98e9b97d-b84b-4fdd-84cb-cd901e9e1ff3.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="18.5 小时长续航 + 左右自动摆头：小米桌面移动风扇 129 → 96 元国补发车" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">天猫</span><span class="card-name">小米 桌面移动风扇</span></span><span class="card-abstract">桌面手持二合一</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">双重补贴 95.95 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">领 149 元券</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p><div class="tagging1">【广告】</div>
